<title>USA: Stevens to sell Bernal division.</title>
<headline>Stevens to sell Bernal division.</headline>
<dateline>FORT WORTH 1996-10-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Stevens International Inc said on Wednesday it had reached agreement in principal to sell its Bernal Division to an investor group led by the GR Investment Group LT of Detroit.</p>
<p>Terms were not disclosed.</p>
<p>Stevens said in a statement that the proposed sale includes substantially all assets and all the operations of the Bernal Division.</p>
<p>Stevens said the parties expect a closing date of December 3.</p>
<p>Stevens said the sale would significantly reduce its indebtedness.</p>
